[section#res.contract.assertions
    [:en] Contract assertions
    [:zh_CN] 契约断言
]

[para]
[:en] Unless specified otherwise, an implementation may check the specified
preconditions and postconditions of a function in the [=Cpp] standard library
using contract assertions ([#basic.contract], [#structure.specifications]).
[:zh_CN] 除非另有规定，实现可以使用契约断言（[#basic.contract]，[#structure.specifications]）
检查 [=Cpp] 标准库中函数所指定的前条件和后条件。
